Beautiful one bedroom/one bathroom apartment for rent in the heart of Mt. Adams! Centrally located and walkable to all restaurants and bars in Mt. Adams. Also, easily walkable to downtown Cincinnati/Over the Rhine. Extremely spacious first floor living space with updated kitchen. Large, lower-level bedroom and oversized bathroom with laundry in unit. Front patio directly across the street from Mt. Adams Bar &amp; Grill!<br>
<br>
Owner pays for water/sewage. Renter is responsible for gas and electric. No smoking allowed. Small dogs &amp; cats are permitted.<br>
